Introduction

Puzzle was a five-member South Korean-Japanese project unit group created by Good Choice Entertainment. They made their debut in November 20, 2023 with the digital single "I".

The collaboration group consists of 1CHU member, We;Na's Yeonseo & Wony members and the Japanese girl group Secret School members.

The group name "Puzzle" means that members of various colors (puzzles) gather to complete a new entertainment.

The group presumably disbanded in March 2025 due to inactivity and several members departing from their original groups and the groups SNS accounts have been turned into accounts for J-pop group Red Radiance.
